@Node MAIN "A Guide to the Star Wars Universe - pelvic servomotor"

* Pelvic servomotors provide bipedal @{"droids" link SWG:Data/droid.GDE/MAIN} with the means to produce
mechanical movements in their legs. Without these power units, bipedal
droids (or legged droids of any sort) would not be able to move their legs
to walk or otherwise get around.

